Neuhauser and R. Pugno and T. Pütterich and V. Rohde and W. Sandmann and S.-W. Yoon and the ASDEX Upgrade team},
  title={Edge transport and its interconnection with main chamber recycling in ASDEX Upgrade},
  journal={Nuclear Fusion},
  volume={43},
